}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "Lunzn" and "r68s_V1.1" are silkscreened on top of board.
===Hardware specification=== *CPU: [[Rockchip]] RK3568 @2.0GHz :Quad-core ARM (Cortex-A55) *Storage: 16GB (eMMC 5.1) Flash *Memory: 4GB (LPDDR4X) SDRAM *Network: 2x 2.5GbE, 2x 1GbE ports *USB: 2x USB 3.0 ports *Power Source: 12V/1A via barrel
